    "body": "The interesting part of the trace is\n\n``` text\npanic: interface conversion: interface {} is nil, not *types.Block\n\ngoroutine 67 [running]:\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/core.(*BlockChain).procFutureBlocks(0xc8200d4280)\n        /build/ethereum-efb52a/ethereum-1.3.5+70trusty/obj-x86_64-linux-gnu/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/core/blockchain.go:697 +0x27b\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/core.(*BlockChain).update(0xc8200d4280)\n        /build/ethereum-efb52a/ethereum-1.3.5+70trusty/obj-x86_64-linux-gnu/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/core/blockchain.go:1372 +0xbb\ncreated by github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/core.NewBlockChain\n        /build/ethereum-efb52a/ethereum-1.3.5+70trusty/obj-x86_64-linux-gnu/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/core/blockchain.go:174 +0x1484\n```\n",
